{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.960", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.800", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im vergangenen November wurde im ZDF ein Bericht ausgestrahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der massive Tierschutzverletzungen w\u00e4hrend des Transportes von lebenden Schlachtrindern in Drittl\u00e4nder sowie deren Schlachtung vor Ort zeigte. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.160", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Bilder waren erschreckend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.080", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben nicht nur mich ersch\u00fcttert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern uns alle."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.240", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele von uns erreichten zahlreiche Mails und Briefe von B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrgern unserer Wahlkreise, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ebenfalls diese Aufnahmen gesehen haben und fassungslos waren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.920", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Niemand kann verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.680", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie in diesen Aufnahmen mit Tieren umgegangen wurde\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.280", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "am allerwenigsten unsere deutschen Landwirte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.400", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich Tag f\u00fcr Tag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Monat f\u00fcr Monat um ihre Tiere k\u00fcmmern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.480", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das haben auch die Aussagen einer betroffenen Bauernfamilie in dieser Fernsehsendung gezeigt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei den im Bericht gezeigten Schlachtviehexporten sind zwar nicht in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.360", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daf\u00fcr aber in anderen L\u00e4ndern Tierschutzbestimmungen teilweise brachial missachtet worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.920", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ausma\u00df der gezeigten Tierschutzverst\u00f6\u00dfe ist f\u00fcr mich erschreckend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.000", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr mich ganz pers\u00f6nlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.720", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch f\u00fcr die gesamte CDU/CSU-Bundestagsfraktion sind diese Tierrechtsverletzungen vollkommen unakzeptabel."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Direkt am Tag der Ausstrahlung habe ich mich in anderer Funktion unmissverst\u00e4ndlich zu diesen Vorg\u00e4ngen ge\u00e4u\u00dfert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Tierwohlaspekte bei Schlachtviehtransporten aus der EU trotz klarer EU-Regelungen offenbar kaum noch eine Rolle spielen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.960", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sobald die Tiere die EU-Au\u00dfengrenzen erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.920", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen gesetzliche Rahmen und Regelungen geschaffen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.000", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die den Transport von Schlachttieren in Drittl\u00e4nder g\u00e4nzlich verbieten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.920", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tiertransporte sind nat\u00fcrlich generell ein sensibles Thema. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.840", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr mich gilt dabei: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.600", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht allein die Vorgabe der Transportzeit ist entscheidend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch die Qualit\u00e4t des Transportes und ihre \u00dcberwachung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.680", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die eklatanten Verst\u00f6\u00dfe in Drittl\u00e4ndern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.320", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in den Fernsehbildern gezeigt wurden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.640", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es geht hier nicht nur um den Transport, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.920", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch um eklatante Verst\u00f6\u00dfe bei der Schlachtung\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterstreichen unsere Forderung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Tierhaltung nicht aus Deutschland zu vertreiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.720", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine Verlagerung unserer Nutztierhaltung ins Ausland f\u00fchrt nicht nur zum Verlust von vielen Arbeitspl\u00e4tzen im vor- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.640", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und nachgelagerten Bereich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.760", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern wir haben dann auch keinen Einfluss mehr auf die Haltung der Tiere. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.120", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tierschutz spielt anscheinend in anderen L\u00e4ndern eine andere Rolle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dort gibt es in dieser Hinsicht eine andere Kultur. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen bin ich daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.920", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir die Tierhaltung in Deutschland auch behalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.480", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die an mancher Stelle kritisierte r\u00e4umliche Konzentration der Tierhaltung sorgt daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Tackmann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.040", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Transportwege \u00e4u\u00dferst kurz sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.160", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sich die Schlachtst\u00e4tten in der N\u00e4he der tierhaltenden Betriebe befinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.680", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei uns im M\u00fcnsterland betr\u00e4gt die durchschnittliche Transportdauer f\u00fcr ein Schlachtschwein etwa 40\u00a0Minuten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.440", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit der Tierschutztransportverordnung gilt bereits heute eine umfangreiche europ\u00e4ische Regelung zum Transport von lebenden Tieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.600", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Europ\u00e4ische Gerichtshof hat entschieden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.520", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Wohl der Tiere bis zum letzten Zielort sichergestellt sein muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.520", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insbesondere f\u00fcr die zeitlichen Abst\u00e4nde der Versorgung mit Futter und Wasser, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.160", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Temperatur im Fahrzeug, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.640", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Ladedichte sowie Ruhepausen w\u00e4hrend des Transportes von Tieren gibt es genaue Vorschriften. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich fordere die Kontrollbeh\u00f6rden auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.560", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ganz offenkundigen L\u00fccken zu schlie\u00dfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und zwar z\u00fcgig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.600", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Bundesministerium f\u00fcr Ern\u00e4hrung und Landwirtschaft unterst\u00fctzt den Export von lebenden Tieren nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.520", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei langer Bef\u00f6rderung k\u00f6nnen Tiere besonderen Belastungen ausgesetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.120", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb sollte der Transport von Schlachttieren \u00fcber gro\u00dfe Entfernung vermieden bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.520", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "abgeschafft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Langzeittransporte von Schlachttieren sollten durch Fleischtransporte ersetzt werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.080", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Position des Bundeslandwirtschaftsministeriums unterst\u00fctze ich ausdr\u00fccklich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.560", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bereits im Jahr\u00a02014 hat sich Bundesminister Christian Schmidt gemeinsam mit D\u00e4nemark und den Niederlanden mit einer Erkl\u00e4rung an die Kommission gewandt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darin werden eine st\u00e4rkere Begrenzung und bessere Kontrollen von Transporten gefordert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "282.720", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass nun erneut Bilder auftauchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "282.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "286.360", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die eklatante Missst\u00e4nde und Tierschutzverletzungen aufzeigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "286.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.240", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist absolut nicht hinnehmbar. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen unterst\u00fctzen wir als Fraktion ausdr\u00fccklich das BMEL in seinem Einsatz f\u00fcr eine europaweite Begrenzung der Transportzeit auf maximal acht Stunden sowie f\u00fcr eine Revision der europ\u00e4ischen Rechtsgrundlage zum Tiertransport. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "316.040", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch haben wir als CDU/CSU-Bundestagsfraktion Bundesminister Christian Schmidt mit Schreiben vom 23.\u00a0November 2017 eindringlich gebeten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "316.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "324.000", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich auf europ\u00e4ischer Ebene noch einmal f\u00fcr das Ende des Exports von Tieren zu reiner Schlachtung aus der EU in Drittl\u00e4nder starkzumachen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "324.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "330.200", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Christian Schmidt hat sich daraufhin direkt an den zust\u00e4ndigen Kommissar gewandt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "330.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "332.080", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage zum Abschluss: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "332.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "335.200", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Solange der Tierschutz nicht gew\u00e4hrleistet werden kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "335.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "337.760", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen kurzfristig Ma\u00dfnahmen gefunden werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "337.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "338.920", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um Schlachttiertransporte in Drittl\u00e4nder auszusetzen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "338.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "339.320", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das muss schnell passieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "339.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.240", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich freue mich auf eine gemeinschaftliche Debatte\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "340.920", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "340.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "glaube ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "341.200", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Gute an dieser Debatte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "341.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "342.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns hier einig sind\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "342.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "343.600", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Agrarausschuss des Deutschen Bundestages."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "343.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "344.040", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herzlichen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "344.040", 
